{"tid":1651951,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界同我入黎 聽晚同我fing爆美國旗 Whose broad stripes and bright stars","createTime":"2019-10-13T13:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T12:50:14.000Z","uid":65359,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f15d80534bc5b2cf806c51abf8e66532e66a7ed6","tid":1651951,"uid":65359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:39:57.000Z","msg":"聽晚係人權法案集氣晚會, 無理由兩手fing fing入去<br />\n大家一人拎一支美國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTomorrow night we will have rally supporting the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act, sure we want to show the world how badly we'd like to see the bill passed. Let's have a US flag each on our hands so that we can show you, sir, this way.<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eNkr67K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeNkr67K.jpg&h=71d6313c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n物資 - You Need:<br />\n1) Printer - Printer<br />\n2) 即棄筷子 - Disposable chopstick (or any stick)<br />\n3) 膠紙 - Some tape<br />\n<br />\n步驟:<br />\n1. Print 正/反美國旗 可以係到搵<br />\nGet the template here:<br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/4EzR1Kk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F4EzR1Kk&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnucVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=cf3266ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/4EzR1Kk</a><br />\n<br />\n2: 剪出美國旗 並係空白位貼好<br />\nCut along the edge and tape the flag<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/yR5s8y9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FyR5s8y9.jpg&h=b4c0d47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 插入筷子 固定邊位<br />\nPut the stick in place and fix the flag by its pole<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/Zm4yuuq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FZm4yuuq.jpg&h=2bce03d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 大功告成<br />\nSir! This Way!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"